column5: Leaving Friday and staying the night in Wawa, getting to the cabin Saturday. Checking if anyone knows a store or maybe a local guy I can get a bone from a moose, bear, caribou, or something I can't get back home for my German shepherd! I swear the dog is a crackhead for salmon meat. Thanks.
Try the General Store with the White Goose beside it as you go into Wawa. They have just about everything there or they can tell you where to go.
WORK SUCKS 4 more days till canada buddy! I would like to stop in that general store and see what cool things we can get.
